  <summary date="2021-03-30T11:07:31Z" status="Introduced in House">Election Official Integrity Act of 2021

This bill prohibits a chief state election administration official from taking an active part in political management or in a political campaign with respect to any federal election over which the official has supervisory authority, with certain exceptions.</summary>
